com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.style.expressions

Class Expression.ExpressionLiteral

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.style.expressions.Expression
      • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.style.expressions.Expression.ExpressionLiteral
  • Enclosing class:
    Expression

    public static class Expression.ExpressionLiteral
extends Expression
    ExpressionLiteral wraps an object to be used as a literal in an expression.

    ExpressionLiteral is created with Expression.literal(Number), Expression.literal(boolean), Expression.literal(String) and Expression.literal(Object).
